#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/linalg/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.linalg.vector_norm:12
msgid ""
"If an integer, ``axis`` specifies the axis (dimension) along which to "
"compute vector norms. If an n-tuple, ``axis`` specifies the axes "
"(dimensions) along which to compute batched vector norms. If ``None``, the "
"vector norm must be computed over all array values (i.e., equivalent to "
"computing the vector norm of a flattened array). Default: ``None``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/linalg/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.linalg.vector_norm:21
